graph TD
    A[Trigger: Prompt/Webhook] --> B[WorkflowAutomationService]
    B --> C[PlanningAgent: LLM]
    C --> D[Task DAG Generation]
    D --> E[WorkflowHistory: PENDING]
    E --> F[EnhancedWorkflowExecutor]
    
    subgraph Execution Loop
    F --> G{Ready Nodes?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Parallel Execution: asyncio.gather]
    H --> I[Agent clusters: Research/Exec/Summary]
    I --> J[AutomationLog Entry]
    J --> K[Variable Injection]
    K --> G
    G -- No --> L[Terminal State: COMPLETED/FAILED]
    end
    
    L --> M[System Notification]
    L --> N[User Dashboard Update]
